Variable: A name or an alias assigned to the data
    Example: a = 5, b = 7, oil_packets = 900
    Rules to Write Variable Names:
        1. All variable names should start with alphabets or _ 
        2. Variable names should make sense
        3. Variable Wording
            1. CamalCase --> Space will be replaced by Capital letter
                Example: oilPackets
            2. snake_case --> Space will be replaced by _

DataTypes:
    1. Integer DataTypes --> 32bit --> 4B --> 4*8bit
    2. Floating Point DataTypes --> 64bit --> 8B --> 8*8bit 
    3. 